Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:34.51,1:00:36.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it'll be a fine sports fair.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:36.51,1:00:38.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It sure does.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:44.75,1:00:45.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:45.88,1:00:46.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go then.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:50.72,1:00:51.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:52.22,1:00:55.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there\nholding that thing!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:55.83,1:00:59.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're late setting up our booth!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:12.21,1:01:14.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Miss Jennifer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:15.25,1:01:17.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave your breakfast here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:19.22,1:01:20.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is it morning already?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:22.99,1:01:25.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a perfect day for the sports fair.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:25.82,1:01:28.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness it's sunny out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:28.43,1:01:31.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You mean\nyou're actually going?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:31.36,1:01:33.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. What about you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:34.07,1:01:38.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you people,\NI'll be spending my days indoors.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:38.37,1:01:39.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going to bed now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:39.80,1:01:41.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:57.09,1:01:58.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hiraga.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:59.36,1:02:02.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the\nobstacle race coming up, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:02.49,1:02:03.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:08.07,1:02:10.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:10.14,1:02:12.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something bothering you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:12.57,1:02:14.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Ito.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:14.61,1:02:17.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about a student?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:22.81,1:02:25.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's one thing to get all worked up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:25.88,1:02:30.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not good to get too obsessed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:49.01,1:02:50.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Ito...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:50.74,1:02:53.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I scraped my knee.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:53.31,1:02:54.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:54.78,1:02:57.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is what happens at the sports fair.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:03.46,1:03:04.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Sakurako!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:05.26,1:03:05.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:07.66,1:03:08.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you please!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:12.30,1:03:14.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Uh... Me?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:29.58,1:03:31.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you avoiding me?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:31.42,1:03:32.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:32.18,1:03:33.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:33.35,1:03:36.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we met under the tree\nthat night...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:36.72,1:03:38.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you've avoided me the whole time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:38.72,1:03:43.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think you and grandma\nare hiding something from me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:43.73,1:03:45.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My dead mother...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:45.36,1:03:49.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and the woman I see\nunder the tree in my dreams.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:51.00,1:03:55.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What connection do you have\nwith me and the Hiraga family?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:59.18,1:04:00.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:00.61,1:04:02.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:09.12,1:04:09.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hiraga!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:27.27,1:04:29.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Sakurako!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:29.91,1:04:32.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is Gen Hiraga all right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:33.21,1:04:34.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:34.48,1:04:37.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just a little sunstroke.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:37.98,1:04:41.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess he's out for\nthe relay coming up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:43.12,1:04:45.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ito, I hate to ask you but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:45.72,1:04:49.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...could you go see how he is\nin a little while?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:49.33,1:04:52.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to make a report\nto the chancellor.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:54.07,1:04:55.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:59.00,1:05:00.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hiraga?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:01.27,1:05:02.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Mitsuko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:03.17,1:05:04.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:04.84,1:05:06.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You must lie in bed a little longer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:09.48,1:05:12.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Rokuhira is outside.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:13.05,1:05:15.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She was worried about you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:15.69,1:05:18.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, lie back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:19.32,1:05:21.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:21.73,1:05:25.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed very\nconcerned about something.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:27.00,1:05:31.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't do anything that\nwould distress a professor.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:31.64,1:05:35.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's wrong\nto have a special interest...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:35.27,1:05:36.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...in a professor?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:37.04,1:05:38.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:38.58,1:05:41.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They all say it's not like that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:42.48,1:05:46.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They don't understand their real feelings.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:49.12,1:05:52.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just simply want to know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:55.36,1:05:56.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Mitsuko...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:58.03,1:05:59.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My shorts!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:59.73,1:06:01.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:01.73,1:06:06.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They seemed so constraining\nwhen you fell unconscious.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:06.37,1:06:09.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You had yourself a wet dream.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:09.24,1:06:10.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:10.38,1:06:12.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For a healthy young man,\nit can't be helped.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:13.14,1:06:14.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:14.58,1:06:19.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...calling out Ms. Rokuhira's name\nthe whole time you were out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:20.82,1:06:24.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your body is so much more honest\nthan your heart.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:24.69,1:06:25.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What...?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:26.29,1:06:27.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There. You see?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:28.33,1:06:29.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Mitsuko...?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:29.76,1:06:31.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:31.60,1:06:33.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a man, you know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:34.07,1:06:38.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't dislike men.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:39.40,1:06:43.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that they tend to\nget serious very quickly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:47.55,1:06:48.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:49.05,1:06:52.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...today will be special.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:52.38,1:06:54.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is part of the treatment...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:54.72,1:06:57.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to fix the spirit\nof a mischievous student.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:07.13,1:07:09.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are naive.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:09.87,1:07:11.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your first time?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:13.14,1:07:15.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know what love is?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:15.47,1:07:20.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that's created\nwhen two people care for each other.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:21.18,1:07:23.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And keeping yourself in control...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:24.02,1:07:26.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is also a form of love.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:28.22,1:07:33.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever considered\NMs. Rokuhira's feelings?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:36.06,1:07:40.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Love is not simply about\ntelling someone how you feel about her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:43.97,1:07:46.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:47.87,1:07:50.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can do the rest\non your own.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:52.18,1:07:56.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After you've settled down a bit,\nyou can head back to the fair.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:15.17,1:08:16.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's happening again!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:16.57,1:08:18.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just like before!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:20.00,1:08:23.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that I'm trying to do?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:34.32,1:08:36.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:36.22,1:08:38.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:40.63,1:08:43.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Mr. Hiraga?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:44.26,1:08:46.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have to return to the fair.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:52.10,1:08:55.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to teach you some more.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:57.01,1:08:59.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:12.49,1:09:14.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like to do?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:14.46,1:09:17.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can do whatever you want.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:17.80,1:09:21.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you want...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:22.77,1:09:24.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:24.20,1:09:26.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can't wait any longer.?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:28.11,1:09:29.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:30.48,1:09:31.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:32.51,1:09:35.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be too rough on me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:36.01,1:09:38.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just do what I say.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:38.95,1:09:40.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:40.45,1:09:42.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No need to rush it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:42.89,1:09:44.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:45.22,1:09:47.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just lie still.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:48.29,1:09:51.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to accept me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:52.46,1:09:54.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One kiss...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:54.50,1:09:56.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One love...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:38.04,1:10:39.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:00.53,1:11:01.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Beth...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:01.60,1:11:02.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How was the sports fair?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:04.24,1:11:06.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Quite good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:06.97,1:11:08.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, Master Gen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:12.08,1:11:14.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,More soup, Master Gen?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:14.88,1:11:19.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't catch any sun at all,\nconsidering you were out all day.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:19.18,1:11:20.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:21.05,1:11:22.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of the story?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:22.82,1:11:24.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:24.26,1:11:26.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I was in Los Angeles...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:26.86,1:11:30.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I took things like Melatonin\nand DHBA, but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:30.66,1:11:32.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But there are side effects,\naren't there?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:32.63,1:11:33.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:34.07,1:11:36.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy's outside my field\nof specialty...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:36.43,1:11:39.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but true alchemy\nis an altogether different thing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:39.30,1:11:41.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As for the tendency toward apotosis...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:41.97,1:11:45.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I've looked into it quite thoroughly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:45.58,1:11:48.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If they can find a cell\nthat corresponds to ''Age 1 ''...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:48.78,1:11:52.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...in the human body,\nthen things would be a lot easier.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:53.52,1:11:57.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal this time really goes\nagainst everything scientists...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:57.96,1:12:00.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the world over are doing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:07.60,1:12:09.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:11.10,1:12:12.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:12.44,1:12:13.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:29.15,1:12:31.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same...! This eye...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:32.46,1:12:34.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as that woman's...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:39.43,1:12:41.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:41.20,1:12:42.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...with my body?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:48.84,1:12:50.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're in here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:50.34,1:12:52.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I helped myself to it first.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:12.80,1:13:14.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:14.50,1:13:15.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:16.83,1:13:20.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a bit too small now?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:20.54,1:13:22.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're a grown woman.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:22.67,1:13:25.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have to wear things\nthat fit properly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:27.48,1:13:30.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why should you care? I don't.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:30.48,1:13:31.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:33.48,1:13:35.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:35.49,1:13:36.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:37.49,1:13:40.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to be an adult.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:48.83,1:13:50.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:51.67,1:13:53.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time that you stop...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:53.77,1:13:55.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...peeking into the infirmary.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:55.54,1:13:56.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:58.98,1:14:00.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:18.90,1:14:20.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,''This evening, at 8 o'clock...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:20.93,1:14:23.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...meet me in the college gardens.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:24.00,1:14:25.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Ayumi Ito.''
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:55.47,1:14:58.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?!\NStop sneaking around and come out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:05.38,1:15:06.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For heaven's sake...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:06.88,1:15:08.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen Hiraga!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:10.08,1:15:11.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:14.99,1:15:15.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:15.89,1:15:16.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:18.52,1:15:19.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:23.16,1:15:24.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:25.76,1:15:27.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:28.63,1:15:30.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you dodge me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:30.23,1:15:31.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?! What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:31.54,1:15:32.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:33.34,1:15:36.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one\nwho was supposed to...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:36.34,1:15:38.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...fall into this freezing pool.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:38.24,1:15:39.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:39.54,1:15:40.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:40.98,1:15:43.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can ask yourself that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:49.59,1:15:50.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:50.55,1:15:51.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:51.92,1:15:53.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That filthy hand!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:53.52,1:15:54.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:02.23,1:16:03.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want anyway?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:03.60,1:16:05.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all screwed up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:05.27,1:16:07.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because you dodged me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:07.50,1:16:10.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you were watching,\nthat day of the sports fair.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:10.51,1:16:12.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think\nthat's seriously wrong?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:12.81,1:16:14.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Going after anyone you want!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:14.95,1:16:17.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's my mother, you know!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:18.68,1:16:20.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:20.18,1:16:22.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have anything\nto say for yourself?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:23.29,1:16:24.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:28.56,1:16:30.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At least give me an excuse!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:30.49,1:16:33.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like, ''she seduced me...''\nor something like that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:34.00,1:16:37.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mother's the one\nwho made the first move, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:37.47,1:16:39.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like she does with all those women.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:39.50,1:16:41.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all there is to it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:41.64,1:16:43.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you're some kind of beast then!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:43.77,1:16:48.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's getting seduced\nby a widow or some foreigner!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:48.68,1:16:50.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:50.28,1:16:53.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do men only have dirty thoughts\nin their minds?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:53.75,1:16:57.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for a chance to go\nafter women day and night?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:59.09,1:17:01.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, say something.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:01.36,1:17:03.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You won't believe me, anyway.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:03.96,1:17:05.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me anyway.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:05.63,1:17:08.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe you if you're honest.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:09.27,1:17:11.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I kind of lose consciousness.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:12.00,1:17:14.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And when I come to,\nmy hand is uncontrollably...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:14.27,1:17:14.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:15.44,1:17:17.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst,\nyou shameless pervert!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:18.21,1:17:19.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:19.88,1:17:21.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:21.65,1:17:24.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you believe me.\NI'm...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:26.52,1:17:27.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...going home!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:28.89,1:17:30.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a minute!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:30.55,1:17:32.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're not finished talking yet!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:32.32,1:17:34.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you want to talk about?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:34.22,1:17:36.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to believe me anyway.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:48.17,1:17:50.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:50.54,1:17:51.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:51.91,1:17:54.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you pervert!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:54.11,1:17:55.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You really are...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:59.18,1:18:00.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hiraga?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:02.42,1:18:04.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop that!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:04.46,1:18:05.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:08.29,1:18:09.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:09.79,1:18:10.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your eye...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:13.76,1:18:15.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hiraga...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:18.90,1:18:20.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hiraga!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:03.21,1:19:04.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Since when?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:04.88,1:19:07.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Since I transferred recently.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:08.99,1:19:11.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting worse and worse.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:12.29,1:19:15.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes it's like I'm not myself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:19.33,1:19:20.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:20.83,1:19:23.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...for saying those awful things.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:24.57,1:19:26.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:27.50,1:19:30.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I do such a stupid thing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:30.67,1:19:35.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was a bit more\ncoolheaded than that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:35.11,1:19:37.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Since you transferred here...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:37.58,1:19:40.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it's strange how we rub each other\nthe wrong way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:45.66,1:19:48.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My mother was my ideal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:49.13,1:19:50.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ideal?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:50.49,1:19:52.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's kind and she's beautiful...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:53.43,1:19:56.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and she's well liked in the college.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:56.93,1:19:57.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:59.04,1:20:03.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, when I saw you on the day\nof the sports fair...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:03.77,1:20:06.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...doing it with my mother...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:08.48,1:20:11.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess she's human after all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:11.88,1:20:13.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:13.18,1:20:14.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...turned my ideal mother...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:14.99,1:20:18.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...into some plain old lady,\nwith all her faults.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:20.99,1:20:22.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:22.76,1:20:24.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...my mother was still...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:24.39,1:20:26.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...beautiful.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:26.46,1:20:28.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Much more than usual.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:30.13,1:20:34.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's what it is\nto be a woman.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:37.47,1:20:38.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:39.08,1:20:40.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I want to...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:43.75,1:20:47.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. I was just\nthinking of something stupid.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:50.32,1:20:52.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:52.12,1:20:55.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll feel ridiculous if we catch colds.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:55.29,1:20:56.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:18.78,1:21:20.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:20.25,1:21:21.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:29.16,1:21:30.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:31.36,1:21:33.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:33.63,1:21:34.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how's my...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:40.14,1:21:41.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do my eyes...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:42.07,1:21:43.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...look strange at all?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:45.21,1:21:47.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not particularly...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:48.71,1:21:50.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think they're beautiful.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:10.03,1:22:13.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You seem so different all of a sudden.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:14.84,1:22:16.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:21.38,1:22:23.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:23.31,1:22:24.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...do it with me now?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:26.32,1:22:28.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:29.85,1:22:31.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...right now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:49.94,1:22:51.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:52.01,1:22:53.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it up to you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:53.74,1:22:54.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:55.21,1:22:56.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm used to it either.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:58.85,1:23:01.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it would be better\nto take our clothes off.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:53.50,1:23:56.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't compare me with my mother.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:17.59,1:24:19.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It seems strange.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:19.56,1:24:21.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're so different.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:22.83,1:24:24.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:40.75,1:24:42.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're soaked.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:42.72,1:24:44.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:45.32,1:24:48.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch cold too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:48.66,1:24:49.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:55.33,1:24:56.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How can I...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:56.80,1:24:59.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...be doing this,\nas the student body president?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:00.54,1:25:04.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I hated him just 1 0 minutes ago.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:06.64,1:25:08.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:39.17,1:26:40.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:41.07,1:26:42.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:04.56,1:27:07.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, not Master Gen...?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:09.80,1:27:13.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's what the old lady calls\nthe curse of the bloodline.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:13.37,1:27:15.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A golden eye.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:15.64,1:27:18.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When that starts to happen\nregularly...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:18.28,1:27:20.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...she says\nhe won't have long to live.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:20.91,1:27:25.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just like what happened\nto his mother and other ancestors...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:25.42,1:27:28.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...with their youthful bodies\nfull of vitality.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:29.15,1:27:30.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Master Gen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:31.05,1:27:32.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...will die.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:32.99,1:27:36.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But we do have all the data here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:37.09,1:27:40.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we can isolate\nthe immortality gene...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:41.00,1:27:42.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...then Gen will be saved.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:43.63,1:27:45.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long shot.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:45.50,1:27:47.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please make it in time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:47.77,1:27:52.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To give him the life\nof an ordinary person...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:52.14,1:27:54.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is my only purpose.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:54.61,1:27:58.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To free him from the sufferings...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:58.28,1:28:00.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...of the Hiraga family.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:01.28,1:28:03.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If only for Gen.
